column4: NSLOCTEXT("[D6FD9573431385E44408CA9CA59F0A0C]", "97E36E034A77C52451FF8583A55FB411", "Just a little more... Come on, one more time!")
NSLOCTEXT("[D6FD9573431385E44408CA9CA59F0A0C]", "EE0FB2D24F1E808952B14BB0DC23C090", "What do you mean? You don\'t have anything?")
NSLOCTEXT("[D6FD9573431385E44408CA9CA59F0A0C]", "5AB8D0A643A9056D41BF6CB0C508E456", "If you have too much time, come to the city. There\'re all kinds of Digimon there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[D6FD9573431385E44408CA9CA59F0A0C]", "D2A51B3849C9605DCC6793A9AC72F03F", "Sounds good. I\'ll go. My name is Patamon. See ya later.")
